  notes: Production visual uses the ProjectAegis Heavy Tank Unity asset packet. Hull-attached
    team-color panels are runtime recolorable. Rts.Core gameplay values are preserved
    from DemoRules. Heavy tank Unity assembly has twin visible barrels and a larger
    silhouette. Blocky Mammoth replacement includes a rear missile rack with eight
    helper muzzle transforms, a boxy armored launcher case without the circular pod
    base, and extra hull/turret detail meshes.
